-------------------------------
* Preparation
-------------------------------

**  TeraTerm

	You need "TeraTerm". See here and get it

		https://ttssh2.osdn.jp/index.html.ja
		https://ttssh2.osdn.jp/index.html.en

-------------------------------
* How to use ?
-------------------------------
**  [step1] connect Serial between PC and Spider

	see
		[Serial connection]
		${renesas-bsp-rom-writer}/condor/README

**  [step2] prepare ROM

	see
		[How to get ROM]
		${renesas-bsp-rom-writer}/condor/README

**  [step3] Start TeraTerm and Open Macro

	[Menu] - [Control] - [Macro]
	Open macro file
		${renesas-bsp-rom-writer}/condor/windows/sdk_writer.ttl
